    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Square-back Windsor chairs with two turned rods across the top, the upper rod either capping the back posts or framed between them.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
